ghost-role-information-n14pet-eyebot-tribe-name = Tribal Eyebot Companion
ghost-role-information-n14pet-eyebot-tribe-description =
    You are a follower of someone, obey them and attempt to protect them. In-case they perish you may continue to serve the tribe.
    You have a knife strapped onto your chassis, which others can apply reagents onto. Be careful entering melee though, as you're quite fragile!
ghost-role-information-zax-securitron-name = Z.A.X Securitron
ghost-role-information-zax-securitron-description = A Z.A.X-linked Securitron unit. You are connected to the Z.A.X command network and operate as one of its field chassis.
ghost-role-information-zax-securitron-rules = You are linked to Z.A.X. Follow Z.A.X directives and preserve Z.A.X assets unless higher-priority server rules apply.
ghost-role-information-zax-c27-name = Z.A.X C-27
ghost-role-information-zax-c27-description = A Z.A.X-linked C-27 chassis. Requires the Z.A.X C-27 whitelist.
ghost-role-information-zax-c27-rules = You are a Z.A.X-linked C-27 unit. Follow Z.A.X directives and preserve Z.A.X assets unless higher-priority server rules apply.
